"  Topping:","1.1 ounces all-purpose flour (about 1/4 cup)","1/4 cup packed light brown sugar","2 tablespoons chilled butter, cut into small pieces","  Crust:","5.6 ounces all-purpose flour (about 1 1/4 cups)","1/4 teaspoon salt","3 tablespoons chilled butter, cut into small pieces","2 tablespoons chilled vegetable shortening, cut into small pieces","3 tablespoons ice water","  Cooking spray","  Filling:","1/4 cup granulated sugar","2 tablespoons cornstarch","4 cups thinly sliced peeled Granny Smith apple (about 1 1/4 pounds)","3 cups thinly sliced peeled Fuji apple (about 1 pound)","  Caramel sauce:","1/2 cup fat-free caramel sundae syrup","1/8 teaspoon kosher salt"